OL,7,FThe attorney general is considering
OL,8,Fwhether judges should review the
OL,9,Fsentence of after receiving a
OL,10,Fsubmission that it could be unduly
OL,11,Flenient.
OL,13,FA judge handed down a hospital order
OL,14,Fto the 32-year-old, who has paranoid
OL,15,Fschizophrenia and whose pleas to
OL,16,Fmanslaughter by diminished
OL,17,Fresponsibility were accepted earlier
OL,18,Fthis week.
