OL,7,FThe families of the three people he
OL,8,Fkilled have reacted angrily to the
OL,9,Fsentencing and accused prosecutors of
OL,10,Fa "fait accompli" in accepting a
OL,11,Fmanslaughter charge rather than
OL,12,Fpursuing a murder verdict.
OL,14,FA spokesman for Attorney General
OL,15,FVictoria Prentis confirmed her office
OL,16,Fhad received a referral arguing the
OL,17,Fsentence administered on Thursday had
OL,18,Fbeen unduly lenient.
