OL,7,FIt gives the cabinet minister 28 days
OL,8,Ffrom sentencing to review the request
OL,9,Fand decide whether to refer the case
OL,10,Fto the Court of Appeal to decide
OL,11,Fwhether the sentence was appropriate.
OL,13,FJudge Mr Justice Turner said Calocane
OL,14,Fwould "very probably" be detained in a
OL,15,Fhigh-security hospital for the rest of
OL,16,Fhis life as he sentenced him for the
OL,17,F"atrocious" killings, as well as the
OL,18,Fattempted murder of three others.
