OL,7,FEmma Webber, mother of student Barnaby
OL,8,FWebber, 19, who was killed alongside
OL,9,Fhis friend Grace O'Malley-Kumar, also
OL,10,F19, and school caretaker Ian Coates,
OL,11,F65, on June 13 last year, to downgrade
OL,12,Fthe charge from murder.
OL,14,FSpeaking on the steps outside
OL,15,FNottingham Crown Court after the
OL,16,Fsentencing hearing concluded, Mrs
OL,17,FWebber said the CPS only met the
OL,18,Fbereaved families on November 24.
