OL,7,FShe said: "We were presented with a
OL,8,Ffait accompli that the decision had
OL,9,Fbeen made to accept manslaughter
OL,10,Fcharges.
OL,12,F"At no point during the previous five-
OL,13,Fand-a-half-months were we given any
OL,14,Findication that this could conclude in
OL,15,Fanything other than murder.
OL,17,F"We trusted in our system, foolishly
OL,18,Fas it turns out."
