OL,7,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak declined to
OL,8,Fback calls for a public inquiry into
OL,9,Fthe circumstances that led to the
OL,10,FNottingham attacks but has promised to
OL,11,Flearn "any lessons" required from the
OL,12,Fcase.
OL,14,FMr Sunak told broadcasters during a
OL,15,Fvisit to Scarborough in north
OL,16,FYorkshire on Thursday that it was
OL,17,F"right" Calocane, who he branded a
OL,18,F"very dangerous individual", would
OL,19,F"spend very probably the rest of his
OL,20,Flife" in a high-security hospital.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/16
