OL,7,FAsked whether he would order a public
OL,8,Finquiry into any failings by the
OL,9,Fpolice, health authorities and the
OL,10,FCPS, he said: "I think it is important
OL,11,Fthat all the relevant agencies look
OL,12,Fback to ensure that all reasonable
OL,13,Fsteps that could have been taken were
OL,14,Ftaken and if there are any lessons to
OL,15,Fbe learned that we do so."
OL,17,FLabour leader Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,18,Fbacked calls for an inquiry.
