OL,8,Fconsidering whether judges should
OL,9,Freview the Calocane's sentence.
OL,11,FSir Keir told ITV's This Morning he is
OL,12,F"worried by what appear to be a number
OL,13,Fof points at which action could have
OL,14,Fbeen taken that would have prevented
OL,15,Fthis happening"
