OL,4,CNottingham attacker sentence too
OL,5,Clenient
OL,7,FSpeaking on ITV's This Morning, Sir
OL,8,FKeir said: "As far as the sentence is
OL,9,Fconcerned, obviously there are mental
OL,10,Fhealth issues in this particular case,
OL,11,Fand the Attorney General has got the
OL,12,Fpower to review it and I think that
OL,13,Fprobably makes sense and have it
OL,14,Fdouble checked by the Court of Appeal.
OL,16,F"But I think alongside the sentence, I
OL,17,Fam very worried by what appear to be a
OL,18,Fnumber of points at which action could
OL,19,Fhave been taken that would have
OL,20,Fprevented this happening.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/16
