OL,7,F"The family are saying that needs to
OL,8,Fbe an inquiry into that. I think
OL,9,Fthey're right about that. I think
OL,10,Fsomebody outside of this independent
OL,11,Fneeds to look at exactly what
OL,12,Fhappened, what were the points of
OL,13,Fwhich there could have been an
OL,14,Fintervention and why it didn't happen.
OL,15,FThat is the least that these families
OL,16,Fare owed."
OL,18,FDespite being detained in hospital, Mr
OL,19,FJustice Turner said Calocane still
OL,20,F"remains dangerous."
