OL,7,FDuring the three-day hearing, the
OL,8,Fcourt heard that Calocane, a
OL,9,Fmechanical engineering graduate from
OL,10,Fthe University of Nottingham, hid in
OL,11,Fthe shadows in Ilkeston Road at around
OL,12,F4am on June 13, armed with a dagger,
OL,13,Fbefore beginning his attack on Mr
OL,14,FWebber and Ms O'Malley-Kumar as they
OL,15,Fwalked back to their student
OL,16,Faccommodation after an end-of-term
OL,17,Fnight out.
