OL,7,FAfter stabbing the pair tens of times,
OL,8,Fthe court heard how Calocane "calmly"
OL,9,Fwalked away, later going on to "lure"
OL,10,FMr Coates from his van before stabbing
OL,11,Fhim 15 times.
OL,13,FLeaving Mr Coates dying in the street,
OL,14,FCalocane stole his van where he
OL,15,Fproceeded to drive into pedestrians on
OL,16,Fhis way into the city centre.
OL,18,FCalocane was arrested after being
OL,19,Ftasered around five minutes after the
OL,20,Ffinal victims were injured.
