OL,7,FA search of his backpack found two
OL,8,Fother knives and a scaffolding pole.
OL,10,FThe court heard that Calocane's
OL,11,F"serious" mental illness, which he was
OL,12,Fnot taking his prescribed medication
OL,13,Ffor, meant he would hear voices
OL,14,Ftelling him he needed to kill people
OL,15,For his family would be hurt.
OL,17,FHe is also known to have visited MI5's
OL,18,FLondon headquarters two years before
OL,19,Fthe fatal attack to ask them to stop
OL,20,F"controlling him".
