OL,7,FCalocane had previously been detained
OL,8,Fin hospital four times under mental
OL,9,Fhealth laws and was arrested in
OL,10,FSeptember 2021 for assaulting a police
OL,11,Fofficer.
OL,13,FThree psychiatrists agreed a hospital
OL,14,Forder would be the best course of
OL,15,Faction for Calocane, who believed he
OL,16,Fwas being "interfered with" by "malign
OL,17,Fforces", with all of them agreeing in
OL,18,Fcourt that the attack would not have
OL,19,Fhappened had he not been in the grip
OL,20,Fof "severe psychosis".
